  <description>
    <p>Fast and beautiful emoji picker. Easily find the perfect emoji by genre or search. Remembers your recent emojis for quick re-use.</p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Emojis from the Unicode spec</li>
      <li>Browse emoji categories</li>
      <li>Hover emoji for description</li>
      <li>Start typing to search</li>
      <li>Select emoji with arrow keys</li>
      <li>Press `Enter` or click/tap an emoji to copy to clipboard</li>
      <li>Option to quit after copying to clipboard</li>
      <li>Light &amp; dark theme</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
